Description: Extensions to octave
DescDetail: <<
Contains custom scripts, functions and extensions for GNU Octave. A lot of
MatLab(TM) compatibility is gained from this package.

Note: XCode 1.5 is suspected to break this package.
If you're using XCode 1.5, and this package doesn't work for you,
you can try Martin Costabel's suggested fix from:
http://sourceforge.net/mailarchive/message.php?msg_id=9286931
<<
